    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__slider__slide_image $slide_3_id__en
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__slider__slide_title 'Burkina Faso Mahadaga Synecoculture Farm'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__slider__slide_link_url '/en/case-studies/burkina-faso-mahadaga-synecoculture-farm/'

    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_story__heading 'Toward a future where humanity and nature elevate each other.'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_story__body '<p>Human development or environmental protection? In a world torn by polarized values, is there no path that can honor both forms of justice? What we sought to create was a civilizational apparatus that could realize a truly sustainable society.</p><p>"If science and technology possess the power to destroy the great natural world, then surely they can achieve the opposite as well."</p><p>Born from this conviction, our research focused on "agriculture" and, through demonstration experiments in Japan and Africa, eventually gave birth to the principle of "Augmented Ecosystems," leading to the publication of our findings in Nature journal.</p><p>"Humanity and nature can elevate each other."<br>A ray of light now shines toward such a future.</p>'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_story__image_1 $story_1_id__en
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_story__image_2 $story_2_id__en
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_story__image_3 $story_3_id__en

    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_approach__cover_image $our_approach_cover_id__en
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_approach__cover_text 'Beyond nature, creating nature.'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_approach__heading 'We promote the dissemination of "Augmented Ecosystems" to end the trade-off between economic development and environmental destruction, and realize a truly sustainable society.'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_approach__body 'An "Augmented Ecosystem" is a concept that refers to an ecosystem in which biodiversity has been artificially enhanced, primarily through the use of plants. It has been found that ecosystem services exceeding those of natural conditions can be extracted from such ecosystems, and we believe that economic development in the direction of utilizing these services is the key to realizing a truly sustainable society.'

