    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__benefit_topics__heading 'Balancing Productivity and Environmental Restoration'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__benefit_topics__body 'In field trials in Burkina Faso, Africa, where desertification is severe, degraded farmland where even weed seeds could not germinate was transformed in about one year into a dense forest filled with edible plants, generating sales equivalent to 20 times the annual national average income from approximately 500 square meters.'
