    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__benefit_topics__heading 'Suppressing Infectious Diseases and Disasters'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__benefit_topics__body 'The healthy topsoil created by augmented ecosystems provides advanced buffering and regulation of ecosystem functions, protecting our lives from various disasters stemming from ecosystem imbalances, such as pandemics, locust outbreaks, floods, and erosion.'

    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__heading 'Driving innovation from smallholder farmers.'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__body "In global agriculture, smallholder farmers with less than 2 hectares constitute half of the world's population, cultivate on 80% of the world's farmland, and produce 70% of the world's food. When these farmers transition from conventional farming practices to environment-building agricultural methods based on Augmented Ecosystems, it has the potential to become a bottom-up solution that overcomes the trade-off between food production and environmental destruction."
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__link_text 'View Synecoculture Manual'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__link_url '/en/manual/'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__bg_image $strategy_1_id__en

    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__heading 'Connecting scattered "green islands."'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__body 'While conventional urban greening has primarily aimed at creating beautiful landscapes, by converting parts of cities such as building rooftops and vacant lots into green spaces based on Augmented Ecosystems, the work of birds and bees coming from forests can make individual green spaces function as part of a larger ecosystem network. When the introduction of such green spaces is incorporated into urban planning, ecosystem services can be enhanced beyond their natural state, enabling urban living to incorporate the same immunity as naturally rich lands.'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__link_text 'View Roppongi Hills Rooftop Garden Case Study'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__link_url '/en/case-studies/roppongi-hills-rooftop-synecoculture-farm/'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__strategies__bg_image $strategy_2_id__en

    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_purpose__cover_image $trilemma_en_id
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_purpose__heading 'Solving the Diet-Environment-Health Trilemma.'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_purpose__body 'Through human augmentation of ecosystems, we present methods to overcome the Diet-Environment-Health Trilemma and explore new civilizational devices where nature and society mutually enhance each other.'

    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__heading 'Limitations of Individual Optimization in Diet, Environment, and Health'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__body "The history of food production stands as one of humanity's greatest achievements, yet it has come at the cost of environmental destruction and health problems that exceed Earth's carrying capacity. Conversely, prioritizing environmental conservation also carries the risk of sacrificing human life and health in an era of population growth."
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__link_text ''
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__link_url ''
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__heading 'Augmented Ecosystem and Scientific Indexing'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__body 'We scientifically measure and quantify the functional levels of the Augmented Ecosystem, providing integrated evaluation across the three domains of diet, environment, and health. By visualizing current conditions and appropriately determining areas for improvement and enhancement, we can iterate practices within the familiar PDCA cycle framework.'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__link_text ''
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__link_url ''
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__heading 'Building Sustainable Cultural Foundations and Realizing Decentralized Social Systems'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__body 'Through unified indicators, regions worldwide can compare and share the effectiveness of their practices. Rather than centralized management, each community can make autonomous decisions and build sustainable societies while learning from one another.'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__link_text 'Learn More'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__trilemma__link_url '/en/projects/beyond-2050-social-common-capital-research-department/'

    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_initiatives__heading 'Our Initiatives'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__our_initiatives__body 'We are promoting initiatives to construct the relationship between humanity and nature as a comprehensive cultural sphere called "Synecoculture" toward the sustainable society to come.'

