    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__dive_into_synecoculture__heading 'Welcome to the World of Synecoculture'

    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__learn__heading 'About Synecoculture'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__learn__body 'Synecoculture is a new civilizational paradigm that places the self-organizing properties of ecosystems at the foundation of various human activities. While utilizing biodiversity on an unprecedented scale, it transforms human activities themselves into catalysts for environmental restoration, building a society where humans and nature develop together. For our civilization to continue for the next hundred or thousand years, humanity must transform from being solely exploitative of nature to becoming a keystone species in ecosystem construction, creating virtuous cycles of food, environment, and health. Transcending the binary opposition of human development versus environmental protection, we advocate Synecoculture as a third path that embraces the justice of both.'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__learn__link_text 'Learn More'
    wp post meta add $post_id _wpf_top__learn__link_url '/en/learn/about-synecoculture/'
